<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><key>Ab</key>
<lyrics>[V1]
 Ra u, a zummi hna, Lunglawm le thanuam in, Ra tuah u, Bethlehem khua
 ah ra u, Ra law zoh tuah u, Van Bawi fa a hrin cang.

[C1]
   Amah kha bia cio u si, Amah kha bia cio u si, Amah kha bia cio u si,
   Khrih kan Bawi.

[V2]
 Van hlaremhbu sa u, Jesuh hlorh in sa u, Van cung mithiang mi vialte
 nih sa u, Pathian sunparnak, Sunparnak cungnung bik.

[C2]
   Amah kha bia cio u si, Amah kha bia cio u si, Amah kha bia cio u si,
   Khrih kan Bawi.

[V3]
 Bawipa kan in thangthat, Nihin ah a chuakmi, Maw Jesuh, sunpar vialte
 kan in pek, Pathian kan Pa Bia, Pumsa in a lang cang.

[C3]
   Amah kha bia cio u si, Amah kha bia cio u si, Amah kha bia cio u si,
   Khrih kan Bawi.</lyrics>
<title>RA U, A ZUMMI VIALTE CH78</title>
<hymn_number>78</hymn_number>
</song>